  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK685">
<l>tokaccollit tūvāta nīkki nakaccolli</l>
<l>naṉṟi payappatān tūtu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is an ambassador who (in the presence of foreign rulers) speaks briefly, avoids harshness, talks so as to make them smile, and thus brings good (to his own sovereign).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
